name: Sorceress (Dragon's Crown)
description:
Trained on animefull-final at a network dim of 32 for 12 epochs.

Use 'sorceress' for the character and witch dress & witch hat for her outfit. The vast majority of art was just of her in her default outfit so it was a bit difficult to separate each concept, I think it's still serviceable enough but there may be a bit of bleeding here and there. You can also have her hold her staff, though that does come with the usual jank.

During training I found that her eye color is quite inconsistent, even in her official art. As such I didn't prune eye color tags from the dataset which means you'll need to specify one yourself.
